The paper deals with computer vision tasks such as disparity estimation and semantic segmentation, which are typically categorized under cs.CV. The paper also mentions the use of the proposed method in autonomous vehicle operation, which falls under cs.RO. The paper extensively uses deep learning techniques, which are categorized under cs.LG and cs.AI. Finally, the paper mentions the use of datasets such as KITTI and Cityscapes, which are typically used in multimedia analysis and retrieval, falling under cs.MM.
